{"tid":1994037,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"[現實版打天下] 空手道總會遴選運動員疑不公 接獲107宗投訴","createTime":"2020-04-29T07:50:03.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-30T15:31:41.000Z","uid":9030,"like":11,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"6723fff1c25cada2a1a59cb73635b7a18c7c9cad","tid":1994037,"uid":9030,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-29T07:50:03.000Z","msg":"審計署今日公布《第七十四號報告書》，當中包括針對中國香港體育協會暨奧林匹克委員會及「通過藝術及體育發展基金（體育部分）為體育發展提供資助的管理」報告，前者列舉兩宗近年的香港運動員遴選風波，包括未有點名的空手道總會選拔問題。<br />\n<br />\n報告中提到的另一個案「個案二」同樣未有指名是哪一體育總會，但指出「2016至2019年期間，港協暨奧委會接獲107宗針對某體育總會的投訴，內容關乎行政失當、缺乏申報利益衝突的程序、選拔運動員參加體育比賽的過程混亂／不公，以及運動員遴選不透明」，據知有關總會為香港空手道總會。"},{"pid":"72aa4406499cd8e1671659b3537125b923aa19ef","tid":1994037,"uid":29080,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-29T07:51:27.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"579fd162b93ec89a4abc614a1a4b4851d6683b41","tid":1994037,"uid":68689,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-29T07:56:03.000Z","msg":"打天下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3773f48e0ac766660ef4f40062496ac8bc347227","tid":1994037,"uid":24615,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-04-29T07:56:34.000Z","msg":"香港考帶果堆搏擊類運動不嬲係咁ga la<br />\n好撚黑暗 講跟邊個師傅 講係邊個館"},{"pid":"0823f3dd9d1a86ac03c03aa20d4adf2526d5ad5e","tid":1994037,"uid":9030,"like":13,"dislike":0,"score":13,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-29T08:01:13.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://media.giphy.com/media/j0SNLj9wZ4vANs8Rns/giphy.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fmedia.gip